144
00:07:03,010 --> 00:07:04,526
Do you advise me to take it?

145
00:07:04,528 --> 00:07:05,861
Diphen...

146
00:07:05,863 --> 00:07:07,313
Diphenhydramine.

147
00:07:08,531 --> 00:07:09,982
You find
murder-by-poisoning humorous?

