168
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,432
Okay. This is a process.

169
00:08:00,434 --> 00:08:02,284
We can look for other candidates
at group tonight.

170
00:08:02,286 --> 00:08:04,453
We are gonna
find you a sponsor

171
00:08:04,455 --> 00:08:06,338
before my stint is up, okay?

172
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,210
Ha.

173
00:08:11,212 --> 00:08:12,244
Captain.

