that's it.

195
00:08:53,637 --> 00:08:55,888
Three times you called
that pager, Mr. Jacobs.

196
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:57,289
Three times.

197
00:08:57,291 --> 00:08:59,808
You said the pager number
was 555-0164, right?

198
00:08:59,810 --> 00:09:01,143
212 area code?

