213
00:09:37,214 --> 00:09:39,798
Bomb-building
is a dangerous venture.

214
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,850
It requires patience,
precision,

215
00:09:41,852 --> 00:09:43,852
attention to detail.

216
00:09:43,854 --> 00:09:46,221
