is nine minutes slow

217
00:09:46,223 --> 00:09:48,223
and his fly
is three-quarters down.

218
00:09:48,225 --> 00:09:51,610
That doesn't scream
detail-oriented.

219
00:09:51,612 --> 00:09:54,279
Ted Kaczynski looked like
a hobo puked another hobo.

220
00:09:54,281 --> 00:09:56,698
